title: Camp WeWow - Games Week Day 5: Wewowlympic Closing Ceremony
description:
It's Day 5 of Game Week, and we're hearing from campers who called in! To print your Golden Pool Noodle badge, head to tinkercast.com/camp. Then, come back next Monday for brand new episodes of Camp WeWow or catch up with this week's episodes on our new "WeWow" podcast feed.
